The,service,maintains,a,database,of,local,and,state,emergency,service,providers,and,agencies,from,across,the,United,States,It,intends,to,describe,EMS,and,pre,hospital,care,in,a,comprehensive,way,providing,a,basis,for,improving,patient,care,and,measuring,effectiveness,while,supporting,training,curriculum,for,emergency,responders,API,methods,support,standard,formats,for,submitting,reports,of,accumulated,EMS,activity,and,performance,data,Methods,also,support,retrieval,of,reports,of,aggregated,data,from,all,providers,and,agency